    <briefdescription>
<para>Rigid transform represented by translation and quaternion orientation. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><computeroutput><ref refid="structnovaphy_1_1_transform_1a074b6b85886aacd125ea8db47cc25f80" kindref="member">position</ref></computeroutput> is expressed in world coordinates (m). <computeroutput><ref refid="structnovaphy_1_1_transform_1a1a88b660d881eab306cb61d9a3218707" kindref="member">rotation</ref></computeroutput> stores attitude as a unit quaternion for stable composition and interpolation. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
